<div class="frg-wrap" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <div class="frg-header" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <div class="frg-logo" aria-hidden="true" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>B</div> <h1 class="frg-heading" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Account aanmaken</h1> <p class="frg-subtext" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Maak gratis een account aan en krijg toegang tot het BLURR klantenportaal.</p> </div> <form class="frg-form" onsubmit="return false;" novalidate data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <div class="frg-row" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <div class="frg-field" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <label class="frg-label" for="frg-first" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Voornaam *</label> <input class="frg-input" type="text" id="frg-first" name="first_name" placeholder="Jan" required autocomplete="given-name" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> </div> <div class="frg-field" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <label class="frg-label" for="frg-last" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Achternaam *</label> <input class="frg-input" type="text" id="frg-last" name="last_name" placeholder="de Vries" required autocomplete="family-name" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> </div> </div> <div class="frg-field" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <label class="frg-label" for="frg-email" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>E-mailadres *</label> <input class="frg-input" type="email" id="frg-email" name="email" placeholder="jan@bedrijf.nl" required autocomplete="email" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> </div> <div class="frg-field" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <label class="frg-label" for="frg-company" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Bedrijfsnaam</label> <input class="frg-input" type="text" id="frg-company" name="company" placeholder="Jouw bedrijf BV" autocomplete="organization" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> </div> <div class="frg-field" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <label class="frg-label" for="frg-pw" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Wachtwoord *</label> <input class="frg-input" type="password" id="frg-pw" name="password" placeholder="Minimaal 8 tekens" required autocomplete="new-password" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <span class="frg-hint" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Gebruik minimaal 8 tekens, inclusief een cijfer en een hoofdletter.</span> </div> <div class="frg-field" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <label class="frg-label" for="frg-pw2" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Herhaal wachtwoord *</label> <input class="frg-input" type="password" id="frg-pw2" name="password_confirm" placeholder="••••••••" required autocomplete="new-password" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> </div> <label class="frg-check-label" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm> <input class="frg-check" type="checkbox" name="terms" required data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>
Ik ga akkoord met de <a href="/voorwaarden" class="frg-link" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>algemene voorwaarden</a> en <a href="/privacy" class="frg-link" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>privacyverklaring</a> </label> <button class="frg-submit" type="submit" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Account aanmaken</button> <p class="frg-login" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Al een account? <a class="frg-link" href="/inloggen" data-astro-cid-jxsrl3nm>Log hier in</a></p> </form> </div>


